# Empty Block

Each line of smelters takes one line of coal and one line of ore, and produces one line of plates.

Number of smelters per line has been set according to advice 
[here](https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=862972621&fbclid=IwAR0XXfxZVWVcj0_DAPYxzbDoIWvCzbH3LVt1Px15jFXWlI6txAJaTIgX4A4)
in order to saturate a yellow belt.

Input can either be from side or end, output from side or end.
